summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Sixty-seventh Street from Eighth Avenue Northwest to Fourteenth Avenue Northwest et al in the City of Seattle by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 19657, creating Local Improvement District No. 1904 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
